    <p class="caption text-over-media-caption main-text-is-center">Caught fish drying on the Sierra Madre</p>
  

  <img alt="Caught fish drying on the Sierra Madre" data-landscape-src="https://news.bbcimg.co.uk/news/special/2015/newsspec_12190/media/1920x1080_dsc00912-hr.jpg" data-portrait-src="" class="section-background-image text-over-media-background-image retina-only" data-autoscale="cover">
